<p>
You can have a wonderful Christmas and New Year holiday package experience without having to spend a fortune—just the correct destination and planning. India has many gorgeous places to enjoy winter in the warmth and comfort and with modest expense. From snow-capped peaks to peaceful valleys, from cultural cities to spiritual destinations, each traveller can find a great place.
</p>



